body.note:
Remarks:

Clicking a record highlights that XSLT template definition/XQuery element inside the
          resource (XSLT stylesheet file/XQuery file);

Saxon only shows the applied XSLT templates having at least one hit from the processor.
          Xalan shows all defined XSLT templates, with or without hits;

The table can be sorted by clicking the corresponding column header. When clicking a
          column header the sorting order switches between: ascending, descending, no sort;

Xalan shows also the built-in XSLT rules.
